<h1>Hello </h1> 

<p> Welcome to the official website of the web comic series Fridge Fever, where strange food become friends.   </p>
<p> Fridge Fever is a web comic created by Timothy DaMour that focus on the shenanigans of food left behind in a fridge in an abandoned house in Michigan laid wasted by nuclear fallout.</p>  
<p> Hence the reason why the food act and talk... Fridge Fever hopes to offer a family fun experience to not just kids but to an general audience as well...</p> 
<p> So we hope you'll enjoy your stay here and enjoy the madness of Bobby, Grump, and the rest of the crew here at Fridge Fever.</p> 
